Description: This enchanting set comes in a specially handcrafted blue box, and includes a selection of fragrances from the Blu Mediterraneo collection. A symbol of the Italian Mediterranean and the island of Capri, Arancia di Capri is sunny, relaxing, and carefree. In the air, hints of Italian citrus and the warm aroma of caramel blend together to create a pure moment of bliss, just like being on vacation.Soarkling, authentic bergamot shines at the onset of Bergamotto di Calabria. It is enhanced by the freshness of citron, red ginger, and cedarwood. At the base, an unprecedented combination of vetiver, benzoin, and musk emerges. The Amalfi Coast: it’s one of the most breathtaking places on Earth. Fico di Amalfi is a floral, woody, and citrusy fragrance that calls to mind this breathtaking stretch of Mediterranean coastline with a strong, energizing effect. Mirto di Panarea is characterized by the aromatic notes of myrtle and basil, it opens with lemon and bergamot. At the heart, a sea breeze accord melts with jasmine and rose. Its intense base includes lentisc and juniper with cedarwood and amber. Chinotto, the rarest and most precious citrus fruit, is a bittersweet treasure of Italy. This refreshing and lively scent is inspired by a unique land of contrasts. Like a perfect memory of a sunny morning walk overlooking the sea alongside chinotto and mandarin trees, Chinotto di Liguria evokes the delightful embrace of sand and sea.This set contains:- 0.16 oz/ 5 mL Eau de Toilette dabbers in Arancia di Capri, Bergamotto di Calabria, Fico di Amalfi, Mirto di Panarea, Chinotto di Liguria

Description: The Colonia Miniature Set comes in an iconic Acqua di Parma yellow box, specially handcrafted in Italy. The set included a selection of 5x5ml fragrances from the Colonia collection.Colonia is an elegant timeless scent filled with a fresh, luminous blend of natural ingredients like Bulgarian rose, Sicilian citrus fruits, lavender, and verbena. Colonia Pura opens with intense fresh notes of sunny bergamot, juicy orange, and delicate petit grain. It seduces with a heart sublimated by a harmonious combination of spicy notes of coriander, combined with the sensual floral accent of jasmine sambac absolute and narcissus absolute. Colonia Essenza is a woodsy citrus fragrance, using only the finest and purest essences for the formula. Colonia Club captures bold masculinity and a modern style inspired by one of the most exclusive sports clubs in the world—horse dressage. The fragrance is a fresh, timeless classic for the stylish, modern gentleman. Discreet yet intense, Colonia Intensa immediately captures the senses with its citrus top notes, middle aromatic tones, and a tactile, luminous, spicy and smoky woody base. With its traditional Parma yellow box and classic bottle, Colonia Intensa is a brand icon; an indisputable pinnacle of Italian luxury.This set contains:- 5 x 0.16 oz/ 5 mL fragrances in Colonia, Colonia Pura, Colonia Essenza, Colonia Club, Colonia Intensa

Description: Fragrance Family: FloralScent Type: Classic FloralsKey Notes: Mandarin, Musk, Violet, Rose AbsoluteFragrance Description: Acqua di Parma's Rosa Nobile fragrance celebrates the preciousness and elegance of the rose, the queen of flowers. The exquisite fragrance opens with soft, vibrant notes of Sicilian mandarin and Calabrian bergamot. The heart reveals velvety accents of peony, violet, and lily of the valley, which perfectly complement the richness of the centifolia rose from Italy. The fragrance concludes with a sublime dry down of cedarwood, ambergris, and musk. Refined and timeless, Rosa Nobile celebrates the beauty and allure of innate feminine charm.

Description: Fragrance Family: FloralScent Type: Classic FloralsKey Notes: Mandarin, Musk, Violet, Rose AbsoluteFragrance Description: A new Le Nobili beauty ritual leaves your hair delicately scented. The delicate notes of Rosa become the main characters of the fragrance experience in which the scent is enhanced by the natural movement of the hair. The formula is enriched with a conditioning agent to leave the hair shiny and soft.Acqua di Parma's Rosa Nobile fragrance celebrates the preciousness and elegance of the rose, the queen of flowers. The fragrance concludes with a sublime dry down of cedarwood, ambergris, and musk. Refined and timeless, Rosa Nobile celebrates the beauty and allure of innate feminine charm.This product is an Allure Best of Beauty award winner.

Description: Colonia Intensa, the first Eau de Cologne purely for men from Acqua di Parma. With classic and noble ingredients providing the perfect equilibrium between tradition and modernity, Colonia Intensa conveys the determination of a  man  who  pursues  his profession with enthusiasm and success. He is refined and cultured, choosing to surround himself with beautiful things. He is naturally spontaneous and charismatic and carries himself with an innate elegance. Discreet yet intense, Colonia Intensa immediately captures the senses with its citrus top notes, middle aromatic tones, and a tactile, luminous, spicy and smoky woody base.  With its traditional Parma yellow box and classic bottle, Colonia Intensa is a brand icon; an indisputable pinnacle of Italian luxury.Notes:Calabrian Bergamot, Sicilian Lemon, Cardamom, Ginger, Mugwort, Neroli, Leather, Cedarwood, Lignum Vitae, Patchouli, Benzoin, Musk.Style:Spontaneous. Refined. Magnetic.

Description: Fragrance Family: Florals   Scent Type: Classic Florals   Key Notes: Magnolia, Calabrian Bergamot, Sandalwood   Fragrance Description: Inspired by the beautiful palazzo gardens of Italy's majestic Lake Como region, Magnolia Nobile represents the expression of natural and understated elegance. Created with the purest essences, Magnolia Nobile is an eau de parfum that reveals the most noble and refined aspects of the magnolia. Top notes of Italian bergamot, lemon, and citron blend seamlessly with magnolia accord, a rare ingredient extracted with time and dedication. The heart evolves with notes of rose, jasmine, and tuberose and the base notes unfold with sandalwood, patchouli, vetiver, and vanilla. The resulting unique and enveloping harmony creates an unforgettable, captivating effect.

Style:
Warm. Inviting. Cozy.

Description:
Lilac Path weaves a delicate story of crisp greens, rich blooms, and delicate petals. Evocative lilac infuses the scent with inviting depth, heightened by lush fragrant galbanum. Creamy jasmine lactones blend with soft angelica seed oil and orange flower.

“There is something very special about spring lilacs; as fast as they bloom, they disappear. Lilac Path captures the spirit of spring and makes it last.”—Aerin Lauder, Founder and Creative Director, AERIN

Notes:
Galbanum, Lilac, Jasmine, Angelica Seed Oil, Orange Flower.

I love the natural beauty of golden beaches, lush palms, and exotic wild flowers."—Aerin Lauder

Description: Fragrance Family: Earthy & WoodyScent Type: Warm WoodsKey Notes: Madagascar Vanilla, Sandalwood, MuskFragrance Description: This fragrance contains notes of Madagascar vanilla that glides through top notes of crisp, sun-drenched Italian bergamot and the richness of Bulgarian rose. It also has notes of velvety amber that add a sensual golden glow, while smooth sandalwood and feather-soft musk wrap the fragrance in a final veil of mystery.About the Fragrance: "From the palaces and gardens to the legendary bazaars, Tangier Vanille opens a secret door that leads you into the mystery and splendor of Morocco. This scent reminds me of the excitement I feel discovering a new world, a new city, a new culture. Travel opens us up to unexpected, fascinating experiences."—Aerin Lauder

Description:
Like sunlight reflecting on water, bright Sicilian bergamot and lush dewy greens entice the senses for an invigorating, luminous first impression. Delicate yet alluring waterlily and soft, exotic jasmine sambac add layers of depth and intensity, warmed by sweetly inviting musk. The effect is bright, dewy, and fresh.

Notes:
Sicilian Bergamot, Jasmine Sambac.
Style:
Floral. Watery.

 Style:
Warm. Inviting. Cozy.

Description:
Gardenia Rattan captures the spirit of summer. Like a breath of sea spray, sparkling wet marine notes envelop the senses, while a gentle blend of white flowers including gardenia, tuberose, and tiare Tahiti exude lush femininity. Amber adds rich texture, like the last warming rays of the perfect summer day.

“Gardenia Rattan is the perfect summer day: warm sun, beautiful sea and fresh flowers.”—Aerin Lauder, Founder and Creative Director, AERIN    

Notes:
Wet Marine Notes, Gardenia, Tuberose, Tiare Tahiti, Amber.
Style:
Sparkling. Bright. Transportive.

Description: Fragrance Family: FreshScent Type: Fresh FloralsKey Notes: Sicilian Bergamot, Neroli Petals, MuskFragrance Description: AERIN introduces Aegea Blossom, a luminous floral scent, that captures the sparkling vibrancy of a coastal paradise and a cool breeze on the open water. Notes of Sicilian bergamot paired with crisp mandarin and glistening verbena open the fragrance with a sophisticated, radiant glow that sparkles. Diffused with a breeze of sheer jasmine to impart a unique luminosity, scents of sun-drenched neroli petals and blooming orange flower glisten with a naturally fresh brilliance. In the final notes, glowing musk surrenders to the sultry, lingering notes of vetiver and sandalwood, as warm as the reflection of sunlight on water.

Description: Fragrance Family: FloralScent Type: Warm FloralsKey Notes: Mandarin, Black Currant, Cedarwood, Egyptian Jasmine, IrisFragrance Description: This fragrance is like an iris meadow that beckons with crisp green notes infused with lush florals and deepened by warm, energizing woods. Mandarin and blackcurrant blend with fresh florals like iris and Egyptian jasmine to balance the scent with vibrant depth while cedarwood melts into creamy, woody musk. About the Fragrance: "Iris Meadow is a place to dream—like walking through wide open fields, under brilliant blue skies, in an endless landscape of wild flowers. To me, fresh flowers are one of my basic pleasures. Whether it's a little plant from the corner flower stand or a beautiful orchid, it's nice to have that bit of life in a room. This scent captures that feeling of life and energy."—Aerin Lauder

Description:
What it is:
 A richly luxurious and deeply replenishing body cream with the scent of Waterlily Sun.

What it does:
This cream drenches with healing moisture to soften and help revitalize the look of skin. Skin appears refreshed and delicately scented with the Waterlily Sun fragrance. 

Like sunlight reflecting on water, bright Sicilian bergamot and lush dewy greens entice the senses for an invigorating, luminous first impression. Delicate yet alluring waterlily and soft, exotic jasmine sambac add layers of depth and intensity, warmed by sweetly inviting musk. The effect is bright, dewy, and fresh.

Notes:
Sicilian Bergamot, Jasmine Sambac.
Style:
Floral. Watery.

A delicate touch of Honeysuckle invigorates the senses, while tuberose infusion and sandalwood add subtle intensity and luminous depth. Ikat Jasmine is as captivating as the woman who wears it. What else you need to know:"Ikat Jasmine personifies a modern woman: effortless style and intriguing femininity."—Aerin Lauder, Founder and Creative Director, AERIN

Name: Ikat Jasmine Travel Spray

Description: Fragrance Family: FloralScent Type: Classic FloralKey Notes: Rose Centifolia,  Bulgarian Rose Absolute, Musk.About: Garden Rose Eau de Cologne takes you into the English countryside, filled with the irrepressible scent of wild roses—lively, lush and free-spirited. This fresh floral rose scent opens with the natural green notes of geranium wrapped around the fresh floralcy of rose bouton sauvage. Like a bud opening, the heart of the fragrance unfolds to reveal the uninhibited splendor and depth of white Bulgarian rose, the rich, full-bodied rose bulgare, and lush rose centifolia. Together, they capture the irresistible spirit of the English garden rose blooming boldly in the sun. The trail is enhanced with the smooth warmth of sandalwood and amber and softened by musk.What else you need to know:"There’s something so natural and free about the fragrance of an English garden rose. The exhilarating scent comes from its strength as much as its beauty. It’s like a rush of energy."—Aerin Lauder

Name: Garden Rose Eau de Cologne

Description: Fragrance Family: FloralScent Type: Warm FloralsKey Notes: Bulgarian Rose Absolute, Coconut water, AmberAbout: Linen Rose Eau de Cologne is a floral amber rose that evokes the joy of a relaxed, casual day at the beach with cool, white linen sundresses and sunkissed roses. Its modern, effortless, and free-spirited scent captures the pure simplicity of a rose touched by the salty-cool ocean breezes, open to the sea, sand and sky.The energizing rush of sun-drenched top notes scatter like orange flower petals among lemon leaves to create a vivid burst of freshness. They flow through the enveloping warmth of the rose-filled heart of the fragrance: white Bulgarian rose, exotic ylang-ylang, refreshing coconut water, Bulgarian rose absolute, Bulgarian rose oil, and rose bouton. Like the sun upon the sand and sea, a golden glow emerges in the final notes of vanilla and amber. Sun-bleached vetiver adds the final modern note of depth and refinement.What else you need to know:"I love long walks on the beach. The roses in my East Hampton garden seem to bloom effortlessly surrounded by the natural beauty of the dunes, water, and sky."-Aerin Lauder

Description: What it is:  A vegan collagen treatment serum that helps to restore skin's natural bounce and resilience while diminishing the look of fine lines and wrinkles.Skin Type: Normal, Dry, Combination, and Oily Skincare Concerns: Fine Lines and Wrinkles, Dullness and Uneven Texture, and Loss of Firmness and Elasticity Formulation: Lightweight Serum Highlighted Ingredients:- Patented Alguronic Acid: Naturally sourced and sustainably produced from algae, it’s clinically shown to visibly minimize appearance of fine lines and wrinkles, as well as boost the benefits of other active ingredients. - Exclusive Active Vegan Collagen™: High-concentration vegan collagen that helps to strengthen and condition the skin to visibly improve texture and suppleness. - Microalgae Oil: Hydrates, nurtures, and visibly restores skin's radiance, supporting skin cells for a softer look. Ingredient Callouts: Free of sulfates SLS and SLES, parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, and triclocarban, and contains less than one percent of synthetic fragrances. This product is also vegan.  What Else You Need to Know:  This formula delivers: Active Vegan Collagen™ to skin to help restore suppleness; patented alguronic acid to visibly reduce lines and wrinkles; 13,000 beads of microalgae oil to hydrate and nourish; omegas three, six, and nine to smooth skin surface; and vitamin E to nurture and protect skin from free radical damage.Clinical Results:  Results obtained following self-assessments of 85 women, using the product twice daily:- 91% said it restored bounce, resilience, and suppleness to the skin after 10 days - 94% said it deeply replenishes and helps condition skin after 10 days - 90% said it helps strengthen skin matrix to restore lost bounce and elasticity after 28 days

Description:
What it is:
 An antiaging eye cream that visibly firms, lifts, combats fine lines and wrinkles, brightens, and nourishes the delicate eye area. 
Solutions for:
- Dark circles
- Fine lines and wrinkles
- Loss of elasticity
If you want to know more…
 The GENIUS Ultimate Anti-Aging Eye Cream is a potent, antiaging blend of actives for brighter, younger-looking eyes. Powered by alguronic acid, plant collagen, persian silk tree extract, and kigelia africana fruit extract, this creamy treatment visibly firms and lifts the upper eyelid, improves elasticity, and smooths fine lines and wrinkles around the eye area. The eyes are given a hydrated, conditioned, wide-eyed look. 
What it is formulated WITHOUT:
- Parabens
- Sulfates
- Phthalates
What else you need to know:
 This product is dermatologist and opthamologist tested to be safe for all skin types. It is noncomedogenic, hypoallergenic, and formulated without synthetic dyes, GMOs, or triclosan. 
Research results:
In a consumer-use study of 100 women, after 10 days:
- 94% reported the eye area felt more nourished
- 90% said skin looked dramatically more supple
- 87% saw visibly smoothed eye contours

Name: ELEVATE Advanced Lift Contouring Cream

Description:
What it is:An oil-free serum formulated to minimize wrinkles, boost radiance, and rebuild skin firmness in 10 days.

What it is formulated to do:This antiaging serum contains a high concentration of the revolutionary microalgae-based ingredient Alguronic Acid. Within just four weeks of use, it minimizes wrinkles, leaving your skin looking radiant and noticeably younger looking.

What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates - Phthalates

What else you need to know:This oil-free serum is non-comedogenic and has not been tested on animals. It has been dermatologist tested and is recommended for all skin types. For best results, follow with your favorite daily moisturizer.While pursuing renewable energy solutions, a biotechnology laboratory in San Francisco unexpectedly discovered the powerful regenerative properties of Alguronic Acid. Available only in Algenist products, this bioactive compound joins other powerful antiaging active ingredients, including a peptide and an algal-based alternative to retinol. These ingredients come together to create a powerful serum that rebuilds skin firmness while restoring its density and elasticity.

Research results: In comparison testing, Alguronic Acid outperformed other well-known active antiaging ingredients, demonstrating superior antiaging benefits. Average results measured following an in vitro test with Alguronic Acid: 
- 55% increase in cellular regeneration 
- 32% increase in elastin synthesis 
- 26% decrease in melanin production
Following a self-assessment of 100 women, within 10 days of daily use: 
- 86% of subjects saw restored skin density (suppleness, elasticity) 
- 93% of subjects saw boosted skin radiance 
Within 4 weeks of daily use: 
- 78% of subjects saw minimized deep wrinkles 
- 81% of subjects saw noticeably tightened and lifted skin

Description:
Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly 
What it is: A luxe conditioner infused with caviar to nourish and hydrate dry, dull hair. Key benefits:- Hydrates dry hair- Improves shine and softness

- Improves texture and manageability
If you want to know more… CAVIAR Anti-Aging® Replenishing Moisture Conditioner is formulated with pure caviar extract—rich in omega 3 fatty acids, proteins, minerals, and vitamins A, C, and D—to visibly improve the signs of aging hair in as little as one use. A proprietary blend of Sea Silk® and an Age Control Complex® help target the physical, environmental, and natural signs of aging and stress that can cause hair to look older and start to lose moisture, becoming dry, brittle, and more prone to breakage. The lipid-rich formula helps to replenish every strand, sealing in moisture for hair that looks and feels healthier. 
What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- Phthalates
What else you need to know: Inspired by the Science of Skincare for Hair®, Caviar Anti-Aging is the first comprehensive line of hair care products that address intrinsic (natural aging process), chemical,and environmental aging by infusing hair with the finest, most effective ingredients to restore hydration, strength, vibrancy, and elasticity for more youthful-looking hair. Every product contains pure caviar from the roe of non-endangered sturgeon fish, sustainably farmed in France. It is naturally luxurious and rich in vitamins, minerals, and omega fatty acids that help restore hair's lipid layer to its optimal state—the key to healthier, younger-looking hair.   Suitable for color-treated hair, this product is free of DEA/TEA, petrochemicals, and synthetic color. 

Research results: Based on an outside consumer study with CAVIAR Anti-Aging Replenishing Moisture Shampoo and Conditioner vs. untreated hair, results after 1 use:- 100% of women saw a notable improvements in shine, texture, softness, and manageability

Description:
Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly 
What it is:A luxe shampoo infused with caviar that restores moisture to dry, dull hair.

Key benefits:- Hydrates dry hair- Improves shine and softness- Improves texture and manageability
If you want to know more…CAVIAR Anti-Aging Replenishing Moisture Shampoo is formulated with pure caviar extract—rich in omega 3 fatty acids, proteins, minerals, and vitamins A, C, and D—to visibly improve the signs of aging hair in as little as one use. A proprietary blend of Sea Silk® and an Age Control Complex® help target the physical, environmental, and natural signs of aging and stress that can cause hair to look older and start to lose moisture, becoming dry, brittle, and more prone to breakage.

Suitable for color-treated hair, this product is free of DEA/TEA, petrochemicals, and synthetic color. 
Research results: Based on an outside consumer study with CAVIAR Anti-Aging Replenishing Moisture Shampoo and Conditioner vs. untreated hair, results after 1 use:- 100% of women saw a notable improvements in shine, texture, softness, and manageability

Description:
What it is: A luxurious cleanser, lipid-rich conditioner, and leave-in cream that work together to restore, nourish, and hydrate dry hair.

Hair Texture: Fine, Medium, and Thick
Hair Concerns: Dryness, Heat Protection, and Damage/Split Ends/Breakage
Highlighted Ingredients:- Caviar Extract: Restores moisture, elasticity, and shine to hair.

- Age-Control-Complex®: Combines caviar extract to nourish and antioxidants to prevent damage and encourage microcirculation; ingredients work in harmony to undo the effects of chemical, environmental, and natural chronological aging and give new life to hair.

- 3.4  oz/ 100.5 mL CAVIAR Anti-Aging Replenishing Moisture CC Cream

- Tames frizz and protects against humidity
- Provides shine and softness
- Improves texture and manageability
If you want to know more… CAVIAR Anti-Aging® Anti-Frizz Shampoo is formulated with a proprietary climate shield complex that controls the level of moisture in hair in the environment to keep stands smooth and soft—with less frizz for up to 72 hours. Every product contains pure caviar from the roe of non-endangered sturgeon fish, sustainably farmed in France. Naturally luxurious and rich in vitamins, minerals, and omega fatty acids that help restore hair's lipid layer to its optimal state—the key to healthier, younger-looking hair.  
This product is suitable for color-treated hair and free of DEA/TEA, petrochemicals, and synthetic color. 
Research results: Based on a clinical study with use of Shampoo, Conditioner, and Blowout Butter:
- 80% less frizz in your hair within the course of 72 hours

Description:
What it is: An instant and long-lasting, root-to-tip, touchable volume styling mist with flexible hold and shine.   
Hair Type: Straight, Wavy, Curly, and Coily
Hair Texture: Fine, Medium, and Thick
Hair Concerns: Volume, Shine, and Strength
Formulation: Liquid
Highlighted Ingredients:
- Caviar Extract: One of nature’s richest sources of omega-3 fatty acids; restores moisture, elasticity and shine to hair.   
- Marine Plumping Complex: A blend of naturally volumizing botanicals, including sea kelp and biotin, designed to help thicken hair both instantly and over time.  
- Age-Control-Complex®: A proprietary complex combining caviar extract to nourish and antioxidants to prevent damage and encourage microcirculation; work in harmony to undo the effects of chemical, environmental, and natural chronological aging and give new life to hair. 
- Panthenol: Provides essential nutrients that strengthen, condition, and protect the hair.
 Ingredient Callouts: Free of sulfates SLS and SLES, parabens, phthalates, DEA/TEA, and synthetic color.
What Else You Need to Know: This multitasking treatment styler nourishes, replenishes, and preserves the health of hair strands, while delivering more fullness and volume. Formulated with the signature caviar extract and our volume-building marine plumping complex, it helps create lasting touchably soft volume from the roots to the ends. The formula leaves hair looking and feeling healthy while instantly delivering more fullness and volume vs. untreated hair, when used as a regimen with the Caviar Anti-Aging Multiplying Volume Shampoo and Conditioner.
Inspired by the Science of Skincare for Hair®, Caviar Anti-Aging is Alterna Haircare’s first comprehensive line of hair care products that address intrinsic (natural aging process), chemical, and environmental aging by infusing hair with the finest, most effective ingredients to restore hydration, strength, vibrancy, and elasticity for more youthful-looking hair. Every product contains pure caviar from the roe of non-endangered sturgeon fish, sustainably farmed in France. Luxurious and rich in vitamins, minerals, and omega fatty acids that help restore hair's lipid layer to its optimal state...the key to healthier, younger-looking hair.

Name: CAVIAR Anti-Aging® Infinite Color Hold Conditioner

Description:
What it is: A blowout balm formulated to protect and cut down on blow-dry time.
Hair Type: Straight, Wavy, Curly, and Coily
Hair Texture: Fine, Medium, and Thick
Hair Concerns: Damage/Split Ends, Heat Protection, and Shine
Formulation: Balm
Highlighted Ingredients:
- Flex-strength Complex: A synergistic blend of strengthening proteins and nourishing extracts that give hair both strength and flexibility to help prevent breakage due to vigorous hair styling techniques and hot tools; pearl proteins reinforce the strength of the hair fiber, while panthenol, keratin, and biotin fortify each strand and increase flexibility to prevent breakage during the styling process. 
- Caviar Extract: Rich source of omega-3 fatty acids; restores moisture, elasticity, and shine to hair.
- Seasilk: Moisturizing botanical blend of marine actives that provide hydration and nourishment to hair.
 Ingredient Callouts: Free of sulfates SLS and SLES, parabens, and phthalates.
What Else You Need to Know: This balm helps to create sleek, smooth blowouts with radiant shine. It conditions and enriches hair, allowing for easier brush glide, reducing blow drying time, and providing protection against damage from heat-styling tools. An age-control complex helps undo effects of chemical, environmental, and natural chronological aging, while enzymetherapy improves absorption of vital nutrients and supports keratin production for stronger hair. 
This product is an Allure Best of Beauty award winner.

Name: CAVIAR Anti-Aging® Rapid Blowout Balm

Description:
Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly Coiled
What it is:A lightweight melting cream-to-oil formula that tames even the most defiant, frizzy hair while protecting from heat-styling and humidity, helping seal in moisture while adding shine and smoothness.
Key benefits:
- Tames frizz
- Improves shine and softness
- Improves texture and manageability
If you want to know more… CAVIAR Omega+ Anti-Frizz Blowout Butter is formulated with a proprietary climate shield complex that controls the level of moisture in hair in the environment to keep stands smooth and soft—with less frizz for up to 72 hours. Pure caviar extract, rich in omega 3 fatty acids, proteins, minerals, and vitamins A, C, and D help visibly improve the signs of aging hair: manageability, breakage, dryness, and dullness. A nourishing blend of Abyssinian, camellia, and avocado oils help to condition and smooth hair, restoring its strength and luster. Hair is left smooth and bouncy without a greasy residue. 
What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- Phthalates
What else you need to know: Inspired by the Science of Skincare for Hair®, Caviar Anti-Aging is the first comprehensive line of hair care products that address intrinsic (natural aging process), chemical, and environmental aging by infusing hair with the finest, most effective ingredients to restore hydration, strength, vibrancy, and elasticity for more youthful-looking hair. Every product contains pure caviar from the roe of non-endangered sturgeon fish, sustainably farmed in France. Naturally luxurious and rich in vitamins, minerals, and omega fatty acids that help restore hair's lipid layer to its optimal state—the key to healthier, younger-looking hair.  
This product is suitable for color-treated hair and free of DEA/TEA, petrochemicals, and synthetic color. 
Research results: Based on a clinical study, with use of Shampoo, Conditioner, and Blowout Butter:
- 80% less frizz in your hair within the course of 72 hours
Based on a clinical study vs. untreated hair:
- 40% reduced blow dry time
- Provides heat protection up to 450 degrees F

Description:
Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly Coiled
What it is: A luxe conditioner infused with caviar that smooths hair and fights frizz for a youthful, silky look.  
Key benefits:
- Tames frizz and protects against humidity
- Provides shine and softness
- Improves texture and manageability
If you want to know more… CAVIAR Anti-Aging® Anti-Frizz Conditioner is formulated with a proprietary climate shield complex that controls the level of moisture in hair in the environment to keep stands smooth and soft—with less frizz for up to 72 hours. Pure caviar extract, rich in omega 3 fatty acids, proteins, minerals, and vitamins A, C, and D, help visibly improve the signs of aging hair: manageability, breakage, dryness, and dullness. A nourishing blend of Abyssinian, camellia, and avocado oils help to condition and smooth hair, restoring its strength and luster.
What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- Phthalates
What else you need to know: Inspired by the Science of Skincare for Hair®, Caviar Anti-Aging is the first comprehensive line of hair care products that address intrinsic (natural aging process), chemical, and environmental aging by infusing hair with the finest, most effective ingredients to restore hydration, strength, vibrancy, and elasticity for more youthful-looking hair. Every product contains pure caviar from the roe of non-endangered sturgeon fish, sustainably farmed in France. Naturally luxurious and rich in vitamins, minerals, and omega fatty acids that help restore hair's lipid layer to its optimal state—the key to healthier, younger-looking hair.  
This product is suitable for color-treated hair and free of DEA/TEA, petrochemicals, and synthetic color. 
Research results: Based on a clinical study with use of Shampoo, Conditioner, and Blowout Butter:
- 80% less frizz in your hair within the course of 72 hours

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:A daily or weekly luxurious, deep conditioning treatment that completely restores and repairs dry, damaged hair.Key benefits:- Deeply conditions and hydrates- Restores and repairs damaged hair- Improves softness, shine, and elasticityIf you want to know more… The Soulfood Nourishing Mask deeply conditions and hydrates hair. The result is long-lasting softness, shine, elasticity, and manageability. Luxuriously thick, yet never heavy, the formula allows thirsty hair to drink up the exact amount of hydration needed.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know: This product is certified vegan and formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. It is safe for color-treated, Brazilian-treated, and keratin-treated hair. Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

Description: What it is: A purple conditioner that neutralizes orange, brassy tones in blonde, gray, and silver hair for bright, cool-toned results. Hair Type: Straight, Wavy, Curly, and CoilyHair Texture: Fine, Medium, and ThickHair Concerns:- Brassiness- Color Fading - ShineKey Benefits: - Purple pigments counteract harsh, brassy orange tones- Provides vital hydration that blondes need- Increases shine and softnessFormulation: CreamHighlighted Ingredients:- Shea Butter: Packed with vitamins, minerals, and fatty acids known to provide deep hydration, softness, and shine.- Keratin: Provides hair with essential protein to boost strength. - Sea Buckthorn: Full of vitamins and antioxidants for healthier hair. Perfect for blonde and gray shades, it delivers cool-toned results—whether hair is natural or bleached. Packed with essential vitamins and minerals, this conditioner makes blonde maintenance a breeze.

Name: Bust Your Brass Blonde Purple Conditioner

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:A dry shampoo formulated without talc or aluminum that refreshes hair by absorbing excess oil and adding volume.Key benefits:- Naturally cleans and deodorizes hair- Adds volume- Cools and refreshes scalpIf you want to know more… Perk Up Dry Shampoo is your secret weapon to maintaining your style. Enriched with natural rice starch, which immediately works to absorb excess oils, Perk Up Dry Shampoo is one of the only dry shampoos on the market formulated without aluminum starch or telltale, chalky talc. Whether you’re in need of a quick no-wash cleanse or an extra boost of volume, a swift mist of this Sea Buckthorn Berry-infused formula leaves hair soft and refreshed, while a spray to the roots adds volume. This product is color-free and contains no harmful ingredients—so it doesn’t leave a dreaded dusty residue, but naturally revitalized hair.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know:A perfect partner to Silken Up Dry Conditioner (sold separately), use Perk Up Dry Shampoo to absorb excess oil and add volume at the root, and Silken Up Dry Conditioner (sold separately) to lightly condition the lengths of hair. This dynamic duo delivers the ultimate freshly washed look and feel.                                 This product is a NewBeauty Beauty Choice Award winner.This product is certified vegan and formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:An intensive, rich weekly treatment that instantly repairs and resuscitates dry, damaged, and overstressed hair.Key benefits:- Improves manageability and shine- Reinforces and strengthens hair- Revitalizes, restores and softens damaged tresses.If you want to know more… Fast-track your hair rehab and give it the fix it’s desperate for. A rich turnaround treatment, The Kure intense repair mask repairs and resuscitates strands. This intensive weekly treatment uses moisturizing shea butter to heal overstressed and over-processed strands. Extracted from starflower seeds, borage oil contains the highest level ever found in a specialty oil of the essential fatty acid, omega-6, reinforcing the hair to make it stronger, shinier, softer, and improves manageability. Full of vitamins, minerals and five principle fatty acids, it helps damaged hair look revitalized, smoothed, and softened.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know:  This product is certified vegan and formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. It is safe for color-treated, Brazilian-treated, and keratin-treated hair.
Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. 
Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:A daily or weekly luxurious, deep conditioning treatment that completely restores and repairs dry, damaged hair.Key benefits:- Deeply conditions and hydrates- Restores and repairs damaged hair- Improves softness, shine, and elasticityIf you want to know more… The Soulfood Nourishing Mask deeply conditions and hydrates hair. The result is long-lasting softness, shine, elasticity, and manageability. Luxuriously thick, yet never heavy, the formula allows thirsty hair to drink up the exact amount of hydration needed.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know: This product is certified vegan and formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. It is safe for color-treated, Brazilian-treated, and keratin-treated hair. Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:A keratin-rich shampoo that repairs, restores, and revitalizes dry, damaged, and overstressed hair.Key benefits:- Restores moisture, elasticity, luster, and smoothness- Improves hairs' manageability and shine- Provides vital nutrients to smooth and nourish hairIf you want to know more… The Kure Repair Shampoo's keratin-rich formula restores damaged hair to health and vibrancy. Hydrolyzed wheat protein increases the hair’s ability to retain moisture for revitalized, shiny hair with improved manageability. Avocado oil provides nourishment and smoothing from important nutrients like protein, vitamin A, D, E, B6, amino acids, folic acid, and minerals.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know: This product is formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. It is safe for color-treated, Brazilian-treated, and keratin-treated hair.Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

- Heat resistant three-fingered glove gives flexibility and more precise curling without the burn

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:A dry shampoo formulated without talc or aluminum that refreshes hair by absorbing excess oil and adding volume.Key benefits:- Naturally cleans and deodorizes hair- Adds volume- Cools and refreshes scalpIf you want to know more… Perk Up Dry Shampoo is your secret weapon to maintaining your style. Enriched with natural rice starch, which immediately works to absorb excess oils, Perk Up Dry Shampoo is one of the only dry shampoos on the market formulated without aluminum starch or telltale, chalky talc. Whether you’re in need of a quick no-wash cleanse or an extra boost of volume, a swift mist of this Sea Buckthorn Berry-infused formula leaves hair soft and refreshed, while a spray to the roots adds volume. This product is color-free and contains no harmful ingredients—so it doesn’t leave a dreaded dusty residue, but naturally revitalized hair.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know:A perfect partner to Silken Up Dry Conditioner (sold separately), use Perk Up Dry Shampoo to absorb excess oil and add volume at the root, and Silken Up Dry Conditioner (sold separately) to lightly condition the lengths of hair. This dynamic duo delivers the ultimate freshly washed look and feel.                                 This product is a NewBeauty Beauty Choice Award winner.This product is formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ CurlyWhat it is:An innovative jelly shampoo that utilizes charcoal, pink clay, and sea salt to deep clean, purify, rebalance, and soothe the scalp.Key benefits:- Sea salt, pink clay, and charcoal exfoliate and purify  - Soothes sensitive, itchy, or oily scalps- Absorbs toxins, dirt, and pollutants from hair and scalpIf you want to know more… Hit reset and detoxify your scalp with this weekly treatment. An innovative cleanser for your hair and scalp, the gentle shampoo in jelly consistency uses charcoal, pink clay, and sea salt to deep clean, purify, rebalance, and soothe sensitive, itchy, or oily scalps. Hair is left feeling ready for another week of to-dos.   What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know: This product is certified free of MIT/MCI, artificial colors, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, and talc.       Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

Sea buckthorn berry, also known as obliphica, is included in all of amika’s haircare and styling products. Description:
Which hair type is it good for?
✔ Straight
✔ Wavy
✔ Curly
✔ Coiled
✔ Tightly Coiled
What it is:
 A travel-ready mini hair dryer, styling tool, and travel bag kit for smooth and polished styles in straight, wavy, or curly looks.
Key benefits:
- Straightens, curls, and waves hair
- Boosts shine 
- Eliminates frizz
If you want to know more…
 The amika Mighty Mini Jet Set Kit is a travel-friendly, high-fashion print version of amika’s bestselling Repair + Smooth Blowdryer and Digital Ceramic Styler. The compact, yet powerful 1,000-watt Mini Dryer includes a miniature airflow concentrator, a diffuser, and a motor with tourmaline-infused components that emit far-infrared heat and negative ions to ban frizz and deliver smooth styles. The Mini Styler weighs less than two pounds and features ultra-smooth ceramic plates and temperature settings that reach up to 400 degrees Fahrenheit with dual voltage. The floating plates are interchangeable and adjust as you style, creating straight, curly, or wavy looks. Perfect for styling on the go, the kit offers a trendy travel bag, included, and a good hair day wherever you are.
This set contains:
- Mini Dryer in Black Obliphica Print
- Mini Styler in Black Obliphica Print 
- Travel bag

Description:
What it is: A dry texture paste that absorbs excess oil, enhances piecey-ness, and adds body for a textured, defined look with a mattifying grit finish.
Hair Type: Straight, Wavy, Curly, and Coily
Hair Texture: Fine, Medium, and Thick
Hair Concerns: Frizz, Hold, and Volumizing
Highlighted Ingredients:- Zeolite: Fights frizz, detoxifies hair, and builds long-lasting volume and texture. 		
- Magnesium Sulfate: An extremely hydrophilic mineral, that absorbs unwanted excess oil that can weigh hair down and protect against frizz. 		
- Coconut Oil and Sunflower Oil: Forms protective layer over cuticle to reduce frizz and breaks down oil-soluble dirt and grime. 		
 Ingredient Callouts: Free of sulfates SLS and SLES, parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, and triclocarban, and contains less than one percent of synthetic fragrances. This product is also cruelty-free and gluten-free.
What Else You Need to Know: A hybrid dry shampoo/styling paste, Got Grit Dry Texture Paste gives gritty, dry texture and helps to moisturize and separate hair strands for volumized beachy piecey-ness. Zeolite absorbs excess oil with a mattifying grit finish, while pliable hold polymers enhance piecey-ness and add body.

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:A dry conditioner that weightlessly smooths, detangles, and restores softness and shine without water.Key benefits:- Weightlessly conditions and smooths hair- Detangles and restores softness and shine- Instantly eliminates staticIf you want to know more…Silken Up Dry Conditioner weightlessly conditions tresses with an antioxidant-packed, dry formulation that won’t dampen a style. This product restores the look of a glossy sheen, reduces static, and detangles hair. Use it on clean hair for a lightweight nourishment and silkiness or use on second day hair for a freshly washed look and feel. A perfect partner to Perk Up Dry Shampoo (sold separately), use Silken Up Dry Conditioner to lightly condition the lengths of hair and Perk Up Dry Shampoo (sold separately) to absorb excess oil and add volume at the root. This dynamic duo delivers the ultimate freshly washed look and feel.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know:This product is certified vegan and formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. It is safe for color-treated, Brazilian-treated, and keratin-treated hair. Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.

Description: Which hair type is it good for?✔ Straight✔ Wavy✔ Curly✔ Coiled✔  Tightly CoiledWhat it is:A feather-light powder that absorbs oil while adding texture and volume to hair. Key benefits:- Texturizes hair with a matte finish - Spray nozzle provides targeted and customizable application - Adds texture and volume to hair with long-lasting hold If you want to know more…Give strategic volume, texture, and hold to updos and ponytails. Moisture-absorbing agents absorb oil and impurities, while giving hair a healthy-looking boost. For amplified volume, backcomb and style hair after massaging into roots. It gives strategic volume, texture, and hold to updos and ponytails. What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates- PhthalatesWhat else you need to know:This product is certified vegan and formulated without MIT/MCI, artificial colors, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban, aluminum, talc, and have less than one percent synthetic fragrances. Sea buckthorn berry (also known as obliphica) is included in all of Amika’s haircare and styling products. It contains over 190 biologically active compounds, including vitamin C (15 times more than an orange), vitamin A (three times more than a carrot), and vitamin E. It also has high concentrations of the rare omega-7, making up 40 percent of the berry. Typically only found in fish oil, omega-7 keeps free radicals at bay and promotes the production of collagen, a key building block for skin, hair, and nails. Sea buckthorn has been thoroughly researched in over 130 modern scientific studies that have found that this berry promotes health. Women throughout the ages have used the obliphica berry to protect themselves against the ravages of the sun and the elements. Founded on tradition and now based on extensive scientific research, sea buckthorn is one of the biggest functional whole food rediscoveries of the 21st century.
